Package: BATTS
Title: Boosting and Bayesian Additive Trees for Two-Sample Comparison
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements boosting and Bayesian additive tree methods for
    two-sample comparison through density ratio estimation, following
    Awaya, Xu, and Ma (2025). The package supports both point estimation
    and uncertainty quantification via Bayesian additive tree ensembles.
